| text   = The Border Kingdoms are the largest open-air sanitarium in all Faerûn–run by the madfolk, of course. Some nobles (aided by large and well-armed bands of retainers) even prefer the perilous entertainment of a ride through the Border realms to hunting jungle cats, stags, wyverns and beasts of the chase.
}}
Conflict is common in the Border Kingdoms. The Borderers have cause to fight the [[Calishite]] armies from the west, the invading nomads of the Shaar from the east and south, and also fighting between themselves over territory.
